# Test Skill

Run the **{{PROJECT_NAME}}** test suite using **{{TEST_RUNNER}}**.

## Usage

```sh
{{TEST_RUNNER}}
```

## Common commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Run all tests | `{{TEST_RUNNER}}` |
| Run specific file | `{{TEST_RUNNER}} {{TESTS_PATH}}<file>` |
| Watch mode | `{{TEST_RUNNER}} --watch` |
| Coverage report | `{{TEST_RUNNER}} --coverage` |

## Test location

Tests are in `{{TESTS_PATH}}`.

## Notes

- Tests must pass before opening a PR
- Mirror source structure: `{{SRC_PATH}}foo/bar.ts` → `{{TESTS_PATH}}foo/bar.test.ts`
